{"id":"8502d6833f2f3309a7e29f519ef1cbf12e989ea953d87933114ea4f79ff71221","item_id":"287f3a54f2:0","text":"Solaris 提供多种 LOP 节点，用于创建和编辑 USD primitives（USD 图元）。"}
{"id":"8cf412a64f63d27a68672c33ee55b2b0f84f03050ac9320e0ae067dad64e35b2","item_id":"287f3a54f2:1","text":"在以下 LOP 节点子集上，除通用 USD 参数外，还会看到 “RenderMan” 选项卡，可用于指定 RenderMan 专用属性："}
{"id":"832bf636e58d104250aee309744c01a79e273f92611ae5b03d0835c3427c4d24","item_id":"287f3a54f2:2","text":"Camera、Light、Render Var、Render Product、Render Settings、Render Geometry Settings。"}
{"id":"b90067850bb0503d710ca8cdf7bcc809c2fff313323b0f8fddc46362f86b9a63","item_id":"287f3a54f2:3","text":"从 Houdini 20.5.486 开始，如果这些 “RenderMan” 选项卡缺失或已过期，SideFx 提供了一种重建它们的方法。"}
{"id":"0ed2f909573c354026411ac36f04ea45cc79695399f09dec6568d7776c327958","item_id":"287f3a54f2:4","text":"可以选择单个或多个节点，然后点击"}
{"id":"f3671bc6515d62e461e24f23e098b275b7e3fd00ae12c9e8aed878b38ad8f9ba","item_id":"287f3a54f2:5","text":"Initialize Parameters -> Rebuild Renderer-Specific Parameters"}
{"id":"21715d2f05d1b1cce271d13116fafc2e8bc84b8828dd908aa4976b0403129d6d","item_id":"287f3a54f2:6","text":"也可以从顶部菜单点击 Render 选项来更新整个场景"}
{"id":"a0e48e9d3a5ad5483a0c673f5fbd0f686a4d7a19d9f2d70cf2996ddc8927c8f2","item_id":"287f3a54f2:7","text":"Render -> Rebuild All Renderer-Specific LOP parameters"}
